            <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #008000;"><strong>Must-Know Info for Lima Free Tour &amp; Meeting Points</strong></span></p>
            <ul style="list-style-type: circle;">
                <li><span style="color: #008000;">How to find us in Miraflores?</span>&nbsp;We are just 1min away from Kennedy Park (on foot).</li>
                <li><span style="color: #008000;">How to find us in Lima centre?</span> Consider if you are not close to Old Town, take your taxi Beforehand, car traffic in Lima is terrible!</li>
                <li><span style="color: #008000;">When or Why to join us in <a style="color: #008000;" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Calle+Schell+178,+Miraflores+15074/@-12.1225926,-77.0319676,17.5z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x9105c818e2e9d1dd:0xdd4b052cbe084319!8m2!3d-12.1226729!4d-77.0306609?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Calle Schell 178</a>, Miraflores?</span> Come to Schell Street 178 for the 10am morning free tour Only as long as you are very very close to this meeting point (Like 15min away max by foot), we&acute;ll take the Local Bus to La Merced church (Lima centre) where the tour will start by 11am approx | We do not tour in Miraflores - If you don&acute;t prefer Local Buses or you are far away from Schell street 178, pls take a taxi and come to La Merced church on your own!</li>
                <li><span style="color: #008000;">When or Why to Join us in <a style="color: #008000;" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Church+of+La+Merced/@-12.048218,-77.03284,16z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0xd81ebfed4d7031cb!8m2!3d-12.048218!4d-77.0328404?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">La Merced church</a>?</span> Come to this meeting point from all over Lima, this is where the tour will begin at 11am or 3pm approx.</li>
                <li><span style="color: #008000;">Where should I meet you for the 3pm free tour Lima? </span>You should come to La Merced church at all times, we don&acute;t collect nobody in Miraflores for the 3pm Lima free tour!</li>
                <li><span style="color: #008000;">Where and When does the tour end?</span> Our tours finish near the main square in Lima city centre | The morning free tour finish by 1.30pm approx and the 3pm Lima free tour ends by 5.30pm approx</li>
                <li><span style="color: #008000;">I am late, can you wait for me?</span> We may! but do your best to come on time!</li>
                <li><span style="color: #008000;">Can I catch the tour guide?</span> Maybe, plz text them through WhatsApp they may reply you: PepeLucho English Guide: <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=51931627473&amp;text=Hola%20PepeLucho,%20can%20you%20help%20me%20for%20Lima%20free%20tours?" target="_blank" rel="noopener">+51 931627473</a> Reynaldo Gu&iacute;a Espa&ntilde;ol: <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=51945467300&amp;text=Hola,%20Reynaldo%20me%20puedes%20ayudar%20para%20Lima%20free%20tours,%20llegare%20tarde?" target="_blank" rel="noopener">+51 945 467 300</a></li>
